*Zabrinut* sam zbog njegovog zdravlja. (I am worried about his health.)

Njegovi roditelji su *zabrinuti* što radi toliko kasno. (His parents are worried that he is out so late.)

Oni su se *zabrinuli*, ali nije bilo razloga za brigu. (They were worried, but there was no reason to be concerned.)

Ne treba da budemo *zabrinuti* oko njihove budućnosti. (We shouldn't be worried about their future.)

Nisam bio *zabrinut* oko toga. (I wasn't worried about that.)